org.graphspace.javaclient.model

Class GSGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.graphspace.javaclient.model.GSGroup

  • public class GSGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    A GSGroup stores the details of a group that is understood by GraphSpace. It holds the information about the group such as name and description. It provides methods to define, modify and delete the details of the group.
    Author:
    rishabh
